      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-fine-mondelez-blocking-cross-border-sales-ft-reports-2024-04-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国《金融时报》周二援引知情人士的话报道称，欧盟将因奥利奥制造商亿滋国际 (Mondelez International) 阻止跨境销售而对其处以罚款。]]></description>
